link:href="gr1"/></fig><table-wrap id="tbl1" position="float"><label>Table&#x000a0;1</label><caption><p>Comparative table comparing results at pre and post intervention stages with Chi Squared p values assessing statistical significance.</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th/><th>Pre %</th><th>Post %</th><th>P value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Patient name/Chi sticker</td><td align="char">96</td><td align="char">100</td><td align="char">0.20</td></tr><tr><td>Subjective</td><td align="char">84</td><td align="char">100</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr><tr><td>Objective/examination</td><td align="char">48</td><td align="char">100</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr><tr><td>Impression/diagnosis</td><td align="char">30</td><td align="char">98</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr><tr><td>Plan</td><td align="char">98</td><td align="char">100</td><td align="char">0.80</td></tr><tr><td>Diet</td><td align="char">16</td><td align="char">83</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr><tr><td>Discharge</td><td align="char">14</td><td align="char">66</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr><tr><td>Discharge planning</td><td align="char">20</td><td align="char">40</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr><tr><td>Signature</td><td align="char">96</td><td align="char">100</td><td align="char">0.20</td></tr><tr><td>Grade</td><td align="char">62</td><td align="char">100</td><td align="char">&#x0003c;0.01</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap></floats-group></article>